|last1=Andrási|first1=Erzsébet|last2=Páli|first2=Noémi|last3=Molnár|first3=Zsuzsa|last4=Kösel|first4=Siegfried
|journal=Journal of Alzheimer's Disease|volume=7|issue=4|pages=273–284|pmid=16131728|doi=10.3233/jad-2005-7402}}
&lt;/ref&gt; Aluminium [[chelates]] with [[glyphosate]].&lt;ref name=&quot;purgel09&quot;&gt;{{cite journal
|journal= Journal of Inorganic Biochemistry
|title=Glyphosate complexation to aluminium(III). An equilibrium and structural study in solution using potentiometry, multinuclear NMR, ATR–FTIR, ESI-MS and DFT calculations|year=2009
